Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:11.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, of course, you only look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:16.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait a wee bit and pick up the ones on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:19.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just looking up isn't enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:22.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Slowly, at my own pace...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:25.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I put my heart into the work I do, and earnestly approach calligraphy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:28.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...I should be able to find my style soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:33.36,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Demon Geezer 2: The Movie"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:34.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is this movie about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:37.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Was it popular enough to get a sequel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:38.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:55.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:01.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It broke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:06.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now what?! Doesn't seem like there's a place to get computers repaired on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:08.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! Kawafuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:21.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:26.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's been acting up since it fell into the ocean, but it must've finally broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:30.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No computer... No mobile... No home phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:35.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to contact anyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.91,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Shiman Ontsuandon"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.91,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,73)}"Translation: Men of the island"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:17.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's been about a month since I came to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:21.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Despite the slower lifestyle, the days here are surprisingly busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:28.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And there's a place that soothes my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:40.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, this place is heaven for cat lovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to pet them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But this is someone's residence...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come here... Come closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:56.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Shoo! Scram! You dirty cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How dare ya stick your paws in the fridge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come now, no need to be so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:05.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyone would be angry if they ate his sashimi for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:08.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, Sensei, something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:13.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, Sensei, you like cats too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you want ta see 'em, come down anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:20.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Before we knew it, them stray cats made this place their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:23.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,W-Well then, if I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:25.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come here, kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:29.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I told ya, they're strays.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They don't get along with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tell me that first next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do with my spread arms...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:38.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why not have 'em eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stewed veggies left over from lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come here, Whites!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wow! Look at all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,With my sashimi gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,those lunch leftovers were supposed to be my dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wow... Look at all of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You named them all White?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:05:00.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just callin' them how they look.\NThey are strays, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:04.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Most people would call them pets by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:07.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What about that striped cat there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come here, Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:11.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Not "Stripes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Black here's the friendliest of 'em all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:18.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The other strays are bad, but this here's a good kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:18.91,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,43)}"※Jikomon = Good/Well-Behaved"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei? Do you want ta hold her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll hold her! Please let me hold her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hurry and take her!\NI can't hold 'er much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But how am I supposed to hold her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:43.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just grab her hard with both of yer hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:48.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:53.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not bad at all. She's a cute kitty even if she is a stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,See, I told ya to hold her good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, my, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:05.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei? You've got bumps around your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wha--?! What's this? Itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My eyes! So itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:14.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei? You got cat allergies or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Allergic to cats...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:18.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look, a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:23.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, Sei. Don't go near animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You don't want to get itchy, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:29.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you get itchy, I won't be able to bear it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:35.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I guess I can't own cats...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sure can't tell until you touch them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Grandma, can I use the phone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:47.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:50.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why'd you come? To buy something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You girls are all over the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:56.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Sensei, you've got bumps all over your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's not talk about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where's Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:02.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's at an elders' meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:05.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you want something, feel free to look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:08.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I just wanted to borrow the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei? You know Akki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:11.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Akki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:13.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yup! Akki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:14.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:20.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Akki's super! He's good at games, just like Takahashi Meijin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:22.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who's Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:28.38,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Only 1 hour a day for games"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:26.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You don't know Takahashi Meijin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:29.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?! Is that person famous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:30.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is that person some Kyogen performer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's an expert gamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You said you wanted the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Akki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think I've seen him before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're Tama's younger brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wow, you two are alike!\NAre you a clone or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Please stop. We don't look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, you do look like her. The power of genetics!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Never mind, just hurry and make your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on, no need to be--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whoa, so black!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, it is a black rotary phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is this? I've only seen these on TV before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:11.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In an age of mobiles with camera and touch panel controls, these are still around...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You got freaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:19.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll be playing games here, so please use it freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:27.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to make an important call, so be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:28.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:36.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What the heck? Pressing it isn't doing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:38.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is this broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um... You're not supposed to press it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:41.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You need to dial it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:45.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I knew that! This phone's dial is just tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He blamed the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,See? It spun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:52.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Of course it spun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can take your finger off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:58.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:02.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Before that, you need to pick up the receiver to make a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:08.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Please tell me the number, and I'll dial it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you're going to pity me, give me some money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:17.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Yeah, hello?\N--Be quiet, I'm making a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Kawafuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seems pretty lively down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:24.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:29.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My computer broke, so I was hoping you could get me a new set.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:32.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't do my work without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:34.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Speaking of, Handa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:37.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of having you take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:42.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's a deadline for the\NNarukain Exhibit this fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's no time to be working, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:49.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was trying to be attentive to you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When's the date?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,September 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:55.02,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Naruka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:55.02,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}Due September 10
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:55.02,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,104)}Handa and Kanzaki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:55.02,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,135)}41st Narukain Exhibit"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:55.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't feel like it, you can let it slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Take your time thinking about--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:10:00.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Send me the calligraphy tools I'm about to list.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:05.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can expect you to take first this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm still in darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:12.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...but one day, I'll find the light. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:22.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So, how much does it cost per minute to use the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm still in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:27.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,One day, I'll find the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Was what I said that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:36.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In middle school, you must have said you had something sealed in your left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I spoke for about five minutes, so is fifty yen okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Using the phone is a flat ten yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:47.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:52.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Grandma says it's free, but everyone leaves ten yen behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:55.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then, here, ten yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:58.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And this should be forty yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:00.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Naru.\N--Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You too, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:07.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And here, Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:10.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Lookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I made one huge bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:16.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, don't hold it with your hand! That's dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:19.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hina! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:26.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They said you were a calligrapher, so I thought you would be more formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sure can't tell until you meet them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like everyone said, you are a strange person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A strange person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can I come over to your place next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:39.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Does that mean you and your sister are going to ransack the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:42.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Go ahead!\N--Why are you answering?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:50.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Damn it... This isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't feel like writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because I stopped work to concentrate on the exhibit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,For one piece of calligraphy, the burden is heavier than usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:06.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I need a change of pace to write one up, or else the deadline...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The hell ya doin' there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ya went and spilled my pickin's!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:15.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I was just thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:18.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thinking...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:22.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ya think that's a good reason for me ta let ya go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's a yakuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I haven't seen ya 'round these parts before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:32.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I recently moved here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're the calligraphy sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:40.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So you're the strange one\NI've been hearin' 'bout!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Strange person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:46.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So, I got a request I wanted ta make to ya, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, where are we going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't worry! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:54.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Forgot my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:57.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Agh, I got caught by one\NA-ranked annoying old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So, Sensei, go ahead and do yer stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Go and write yer heart out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:08.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I guess you ran out of luck being caught by my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:13.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After I spoke about you, he was enthused to have you write the ship's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:15.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So that's your dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I give up already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:21.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Doesn't feel like I have a chance to make a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:26.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Dad's pretty scary when he gets mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's the name of the ship?\NBy custom, is it "Miwamaru"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A guy running a saké store bought the ship as a pastime...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...so I'm not letting him use my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.30,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Small Vessel Registration Examination Form
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.30,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(359,76)}Vessel Name: Yuigadokusonmaru
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.30,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,104)}Vessel Owner: Yamamura Iwao"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's got weird taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:43.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm so glad Mom named me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:45.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's "Yuigadokuson"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:48.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hah! It means that I'm a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--I'm so embarrassed...\N--Like father, like daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:55.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Five kanji characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:14:00.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The ship's body is curved, so it's hard to scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:03.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The tools are different from the ones I use too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:08.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even without the pressure from Pops, I can't fail here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look, paint!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:20.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The paint's gonna melt your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wash 'em...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:28.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I need a draft, so I'll go back home and write one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:36.40,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Yuigadokusonmaru"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:33.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,First, I'll cut out the words I wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then I'll paint over them, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hold it there, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That ain't different from a ship's sheet metal tracin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:42.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want my own original ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:45.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if you want that, the tools aren't what I usually use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Plus I'm writing on something other than paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:50.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you want a proper ship, you should ask a specialist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?! So what yer tellin' me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:56.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...is you can't do it, and want me ta drive an ugly mass-produced ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:15:00.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's not it! If I make a mistake, that'll make it look worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You gonna make a mistake, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:06.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, no, but there's always a slight chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If it's just a slight chance, then no worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and write!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:12.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like I said...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are pros supposed ta refuse work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll decide what's ugly or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:23.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'd rather have Naru do the writin' than sail this ship with a slapped-on printout!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay! Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:30.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm here with a lifeboat to save this sinking ship! Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Dad, it's time for the saké deliveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, go ahead and write what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The heck are you sayin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What I want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Whaddya mean, "what he wants"?!\N--Just like usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,C'mon, you're a saké store owner, so do that job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:46.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What does she mean, "usual"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:50.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That yakuza of a father got me completely cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:54.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I'm not the type to go cowering after being told all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:57.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to make him weep with gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But first, I've got to get used to using this brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:06.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! I can't get all the paint off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My hand is gonna melt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:11.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Your hands aren't going to melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:14.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyways, is there anything\NI can use to draft on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! There's a lot of boards here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:21.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This should be enough to do some drafts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:24.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:25.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What were their names?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey! It goes on pretty smoothly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naru wants to write too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:36.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Jackal Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm finally getting used to using this brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.93,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Stomach Wrap Frankenstein"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:48.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I guess I can't hold in what's on my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.84,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Yakuza Father Demon"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm writing well now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.00,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Yuigadokusonmaru (lol) Yakuza"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:50.60,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Demon Geezer Phantom Yakuza"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:02.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait! I didn't take the curve of the ship into consideration!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:06.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No! If I do it now... I'll fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:13.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But my neck...! That was close, but my neck hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I forgot to check the ship's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:18.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I almost failed there! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right... This spot should do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:25.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Don't push me!\N--Not gonna do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:29.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Damn it! Why can't I do this?!\NAfter all those drafts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:34.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Brush or not, just writing on the white surface is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Am I going to mess this up...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Agh! This isn't going to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:41.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You okay, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You better hurry, or Miwa-{\i1}nee{\i0}'s gonna come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:46.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Shut up! You're distracting me! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:50.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Damn it, I don't want to...! So scary...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--He said, "don't want to"?\N--Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:55.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Calm down... Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've faced pressure like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:01.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I prefer to take my time, but no matter the circumstances, I've always delivered the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:10.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I got first dibs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm gonna do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Me too!\N--Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:23.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!\NYou brats! Brats! Brats!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:26.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look at what you've done! It's all dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, Sensei said "don't want to"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyways, I have to cover the handprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Eew! It splattered all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just hold on! It's the same for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:45.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I don't do it this hard,\NI can't cover up the handprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:47.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naru! Fill the bowl with paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:48.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:50.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hina, your clothes are going to get dirty, so step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:54.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kenta, put paper on any spots where it looks like ink will drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is so weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After all that fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:05.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...I can't feel the pressure, and even the brush runs smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:10.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And all it took... was a small handprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:12.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hurry and hold it! I need more paint!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's sure enjoyin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:22.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The Village Leader was sayin' he works with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I guess he was tellin' the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here, seaweed. It's for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um... This much...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:33.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Isn't this what you just picked earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How do you eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:38.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now that's some mighty good work you did there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll call ya when I launch this baby, so you better come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:43.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't believe he's that happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:46.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's a good thing I asked ya, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:49.95,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Yuigadokusonmaru"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:50.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's way more than what I wanted for my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:52.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:55.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naru's handprint is over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:20:00.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not often I can write on a ship, so this was a great experience for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:04.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I also found out that I can ease myself thinking I'm dirtying white paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:09.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for letting me handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Same here. Thank ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:13.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:16.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seems like ya had a lot ya wanted ta say 'bout me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?! Why, all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:24.42,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Demon Geezer Phantom Yakuza"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:24.42,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}"Yuigadokusonmaru (lol) Yakuza"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:24.42,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,104)}"Yakuza Father Demon"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:24.42,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,138)}"Stomach Wrap Frankenstein"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whoops, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:28.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Plus, I use them planks for gettin' from the ship ta the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:30.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whatcha gonna do 'bout this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:32.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I●●● I●●●
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:33.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:34.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey! He's running!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:38.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What a grown-up!\NHe's even dropping the seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! Seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Seaweed!\N--Seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:44.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:19.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look at the trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:22.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, some of 'em who come to fish dumped it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:24.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Keep warnin' 'em, but they don't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:28.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why not put up a sign with a spin on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:31.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"The trash you dumped spells doom for the Earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:34.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Too large-scale. Doesn't seem realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:36.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Don't throw trash, you trash."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:38.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That'll only make the reader angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:39.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"You'll die if you dump here."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.89,0:22:41.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Low quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:43.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then you think of one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.86,0:22:48.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"If you dump here, a part of you that you can't show others will ooze pus."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:49.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:50.26,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Throwing trash here will make
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:50.26,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}all the crayfish go away."
